{"tid":1716441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"入境處澄清網上謠言","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:44:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df31816f9dc8c2293a785b953b0706398eef357b","tid":1716441,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"入境處澄清網上謠言<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就網上有傳聞指因公共交通服務受阻，入境事務處（入境處）拒絕沒有持有禁區許可證的香港居民經陸路管制站進入香港一事，入境處今日（十一月十三日）強調絕無此事。入境處各管制站會如常為所有旅客提供出入境服務。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年11月13日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間18時05分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/13/P2019111300686.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F13%2FP2019111300686.htm&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=6e8429b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/13/P2019111300686.htm</a>"}]}